channel.title: No "bin" folder located inside my JDK installment?
channel.description:
WTF?
What do I do now? I installed JDK version 7 update 5 and I look at my programs and the JDK is there but when I look in the folder no "bin" folder is inside. What do I do?

item.title: No "bin" folder located inside my JDK installment?
item.dc:creator: @gara494 gara494
item.description:
@gara494 wrote:

reinstall it, starting from the http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk-7u3-download-1501626.html. Make sure you’re downloading the right installer for your system
